---
const registerUrl = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_APP_REGISTER_URL ?? '#';
---

<section class="audience section" id="audience" aria-label="מי זה בשבילנו?">
  <div class="container audience__inner">

    <!-- Text column — DOM-first = RTL-start = visually on the right -->
    <div class="audience__text animate-on-scroll">
      <h2>לא בטוחים שזה<br />מתאים לכם?</h2>
      <p>בואו לגלות איך זה יכול לשפר ולייעל את החיים שלכם</p>
      <a href="#pricing" class="btn audience__cta">הרשמה ←</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards column — DOM-second = RTL-end = visually on the left -->
    <div class="audience__cards">

      <div class="audience__card audience__card--home animate-on-scroll delay-1">
        <div class="audience__card-desktop">
          <div class="audience__card-text">
            <h3 class="audience__card-title">לבית</h3>
            <ul class="audience__features">
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>מעקב אחר הוצאות והכנסות</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>ניהול תקציב פשוט ונוח</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>ריכוז כל המידע הפיננסי במקום אחד</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <img
            src="/images/person-home.png"
            alt="משפחה מנהלת תקציב בית עם KeepInTax"
            width="300"
            height="310"
            loading="lazy"
            class="audience__photo audience__photo--home"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="audience__card-mobile">
          <div class="audience__card-mobile-text audience__card-mobile-text--mobile-home">
            <h3 class="audience__card-title">לבית</h3>
            <ul class="audience__features audience__features--mobile">
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>מעקב אחר הוצאות והכנסות</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>ניהול תקציב פשוט ונוח</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>ריכוז כל המידע הפיננסי במקום אחד</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <img
            src="/images/person-home.png"
            alt="משפחה מנהלת תקציב בית עם KeepInTax"
            width="300"
            height="310"
            loading="lazy"
            class="audience__photo-mobile audience__photo-mobile--home"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="audience__card audience__card--business animate-on-scroll delay-2">
        <div class="audience__card-desktop">
          <div class="audience__card-text">
            <h3 class="audience__card-title">לעסק</h3>
            <ul class="audience__features">
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>הפקת חשבוניות וקבלות</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>מעקב אחר הכנסות והוצאות</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>חיבור לבנקאות פתוחה ולאשראי</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>שמירת מסמכים וקבלות בענן</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>הפקת דוחות</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>אפשרות לעבודה עצמאית או עם ייצוג</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <img
            src="/images/person-business.png"
            alt="איש עסקים משתמש ב-KeepInTax"
            width="280"
            height="320"
            loading="lazy"
            class="audience__photo audience__photo--business"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="audience__card-mobile">
          <div class="audience__card-mobile-text audience__card-mobile-text--business">
            <h3 class="audience__card-title">לעסק</h3>
            <ul class="audience__features audience__features--mobile">
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>הפקת חשבוניות וקבלות</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>מעקב אחר הכנסות והוצאות</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>חיבור לבנקאות פתוחה ולאשראי</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>שמירת מסמכים וקבלות בענן</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>הפקת דוחות</li>
              <li><span class="audience__feature-marker" aria-hidden="true"></span>אפשרות לעבודה עצמאית או עם ייצוג</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <img
            src="/images/person-business.png"
            alt="איש עסקים משתמש ב-KeepInTax"
            width="280"
            height="320"
            loading="lazy"
            class="audience__photo-mobile audience__photo-mobile--business"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .audience {
    position: relative;
    background-image: url(/images/Vector.svg);
    background-color: var(--color-audience-bg);
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: bottom center;
    background-size: auto 100%;
  }

  .audience__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 2fr;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .audience__text h2 {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .audience__text p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.125rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 28ch;
  }

  .audience__cta {
    background-color: #fff;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(26, 37, 81, 0.12);
  }

  .audience__cta:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    filter: brightness(0.98);
  }

  .audience__cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .audience__card {
    background: #EBFD71;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
  }

  .audience__card-desktop {
    display: block;
  }

  .audience__card-mobile {
    display: none;
  }

  /* Title + list sit above the photography */
  .audience__card-text {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding-right: 11.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .audience__card-title {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }

  .audience__features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Bullet on the visual right (inline-start in RTL) — small tilted squares, fill = section bg */
  .audience__features li {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.45;
    padding-block: 0.35rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 7px 1fr;
    column-gap: 0.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .audience__features li::before {
    content: none !important;
    display: none !important;
  }

  .audience__feature-marker {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 1px;
    background: var(--color-audience-bg);
    margin-top: calc((1.45em - 7px) / 2);
    transform: rotate(-45deg);
  }

  .audience__photo {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 1;
    bottom: 0;
    width: auto;
    max-width: none;
    object-fit: contain;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .audience__photo--business {
    height: 117%;
    left: auto;
    right: -9%;
    transform: none;
    top: 16%;
  }

  .audience__photo--home {
    height: 131%;
    right: auto;
    left: 12%;
    top: -2%;
    transform: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .audience__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .audience__text {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .audience__text p {
      max-width: none;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .audience__text .btn {
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .audience__cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .audience__card {
      aspect-ratio: unset;
      padding-top: 0;
      height: 360px;
    }

    .audience__card-desktop {
      display: none !important;
    }

    .audience__card-mobile {
      display: block !important;
      position: relative;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .audience__photo-mobile {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      width: auto;
      max-width: none;
      object-fit: contain;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .audience__photo-mobile--home {
      height: 90%;
      top: 25%;
      left: 8vh;
    }

    .audience__photo-mobile--business {
      height: 124%;
      right: 34vw;
      top: 14vh;
    }

    .audience__card-mobile-text {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .audience__card-mobile-text--mobile-home {
      padding: 1rem 2rem 0.5rem;
    }

    .audience__card-mobile-text--business {
      padding: 1rem 2rem 0.5rem 30%;
    }

    .audience__features--mobile li {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .audience {
      background-size: 216% auto;
      background-position: 42% 0%;
    }
  }
</style>
